TEXT 2184 1520 Left 2 !.param VIN=9.6\n.ac dec 1000 10 1Meg\n \n.meas AC fc WHEN db(V(VACM)/V(OUT))=0\n.meas AC pm FIND (phase(V(VACM)/V(OUT))+180) WHEN db(V(VACM)/V(OUT))=0\n.meas AC fgm WHEN (phase(V(VACM)/V(OUT))+180)=0\n.meas AC gm FIND (-db(V(VACM)/V(OUT))) WHEN (phase(V(VACM)/V(OUT))+180)=0
TEXT 2192 1800 Left 2 ;INJECTION: VAC (DC=0, AC=1) series between VOUT and R3 top (Middlebrook voltage injection)
TEXT 2192 1824 Left 2 ;VACP = OUT (VOUT bus, VAC + terminal) | VACM = R3 top (feedback input, VAC - terminal)
TEXT 2192 1848 Left 2 ;Loop gain T = V(VACM)/V(OUT) | Phase margin PM = pm result (already +180 applied) | Gain margin GM = gm result [dB]
TEXT 2192 1872 Left 2 ;Bode plot: plot db(V(VACM)/V(OUT)) and phase(V(VACM)/V(OUT)) on separate Y axes
TEXT 2192 1896 Left 2 ;Expected: fc = 2-8 kHz | PM > 45 deg | GM > 6 dB | RHPZ limit = 39.2 kHz (fc target < 7.84 kHz)
TEXT 2192 1920 Left 2 ;BOM Cap Bank: C1a=6x22uF (132uF/0.21mOhm) + C1b=2x10uF (20uF/1.25mOhm) | VIN=9.6V | Iload=2A DC (fixed for AC OP)
TEXT 2192 1944 Left 2 ;File: LTC1871_AC_LoopGain.asc | Rev: 1-Apr-2026 | Based on: LTC1871_BOM_Caps_Rev4.asc
